<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<ContentPage xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
             x:Class="Pinochle_Scoring_App.MainPage">

    <ScrollView>
        <VerticalStackLayout Padding="30">

            <Label HorizontalOptions="Center" FontSize="Medium">
Players: 4 (2 teams)
Deck: 48 cards (9–A, two of each suit)
Rank: A 10 K Q J 9

1. Deal and Bid
Deal 12 cards each
Starting left of dealer, bid or pass
Highest bid wins, sets trump, leads first
Bid = minimum points to make
2. Meld
All players show meld
Score immediately; cards stay in hand
                
Common Melds:
Run (A-10-K-Q-J trump) = 15
Marriage (K+Q) = 2 (trump = 4)
Pinochle (Q♠ J♦) = 4
Aces/Kings/Queens/Jacks around = 10/8/6/4
3. Play Tricks
Must follow suit
If not, play trump
Must win if able
Trick winner leads next
4. Score
Trick points: A=1, K=1, 10=1, last trick=1 (25 total)
                
Bidding team:
Makes bid → scores all points
Fails bid → loses bid amount
First team to 150 or 250 wins
            </Label> 
                <Button Text="Start New Game" 
                      Clicked="OnStartNewGameButtonClicked"
                        Margin="5,5,5,5"
                        BackgroundColor="#193829"/>
        </VerticalStackLayout>
    </ScrollView>

</ContentPage>
